=== Verb ===
'''break''' ([[breaks]], [[broke]], [[broken]], [[breaking]])

# end up in many pieces ''(intransitive)''
#: "The vase fell to the floor and broke into a thousand pieces."
# make end up in many pieces ''(transitive'')
#: "He broke the vase."
# stop functioning
# stop working temporarily
#: "Let's break for lunch."

